{"info":{"_postman_id":"cd767856-0f06-4261-a97b-dd6436d6398c","name":"Kratos Pay - Payment API","description":"<html><head></head><body><h3 id=\"welcome-to-kratos-pay-👋\">Welcome to Kratos Pay 👋</h3>\n<p>========================</p>\n<h2 id=\"we-simplify-the-complexed\">\"We simplify the complexed\"</h2>\n<h1 id=\"note\">Note:</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>After demand valdiation, a single wallet is attribute to your account, all transactions are souly made within this wallet.</li>\n<li>Every transaction is subject to a commission, which can vary (visit our website for more info on our commissions)</li>\n<li>A threshold of 5_000_000 xaf is placed for every transactions</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This documentation provides you with the required APIs to access our payment aggregator service\n For authorised request, an API_KEY will be needed.</p>\n<p> Steps to access your API_KEY:\n 1- Submit your marchand demand to our platform for validation\n 2- After validation, use the /auth/generate-otp/{otp} to generate an otp code (to verify your number)\n 3- The validate-otp end-point will give you the necessary access data</p>\n<p> BASE_URL: <a href=\"https://backendpay.kratospay.com\">https://backendpay.kratospay.com</a></p>\n<p> Support: +237 694124760</p>\n<p> PS: Happy coding 👨‍💻</p>\n</body></html>","schema":"https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.0.0/collection.json","toc":[{"content":"Note:","slug":"note"}],"owner":"32753225","collectionId":"cd767856-0f06-4261-a97b-dd6436d6398c","publishedId":"2sBXqQExRJ","public":true,"customColor":{"top-bar":"FFFFFF","right-sidebar":"303030","highlight":"FF6C37"},"publishDate":"2026-05-13T10:21:33.000Z"},"item":[{"name":"auth","item":[{"name":"generate-otp","id":"a74f5e93-e921-4d18-868c-fab3d6fc4be6","protocolProfileBehavior":{"disableBodyPruning":true},"request":{"method":"GET","header":[],"body":{"mode":"raw","raw":"","options":{"raw":{"language":"json"}}},"url":"/api/auth/generate-otp/698483040?mode=whatsapp","urlObject":{"path":["api","auth",